# Milestones:

1. Project initiation and planning
   - Define project scope and objectives
   - Identify stakeholders and establish communication channels
   - Develop project timeline and allocate resources
   - Set up project management tools and repositories

2. System design and architecture
   - Design system architecture and database schema
   - Define API endpoints and data models
   - Create wireframes and mockups for user interface
   - Finalize color scheme, typography, and layout

3. Development
   - Set up development environment and tools
   - Develop backend services and API
   - Develop frontend components and pages
   - Implement token management and blockchain integration
   - Integrate with corporate systems

4. Testing and quality assurance
   - Develop test cases and scenarios
   - Perform unit, integration, and system testing
   - Conduct performance, security, and accessibility testing
   - Address and resolve identified issues

5. Deployment and integration
   - Set up production environment and tools
   - Deploy application to cloud services
   - Configure containerization and orchestration
   - Implement CI/CD pipeline
   - Integrate with existing IT infrastructure

6. User training and documentation
   - Develop user manuals and guides
   - Conduct training sessions for employees and managers
   - Provide ongoing support and assistance

7. Monitoring and maintenance
   - Monitor system performance and usage
   - Perform regular maintenance and updates
   - Address and resolve any issues or bugs
   - Implement feature enhancements and improvements

# Timeline:

1. Project initiation and planning: 2 weeks
2. System design and architecture: 4 weeks
3. Development: 12 weeks
4. Testing and quality assurance: 4 weeks
5. Deployment and integration: 2 weeks
6. User training and documentation: 2 weeks
7. Monitoring and maintenance: Ongoing

Total estimated project duration: 26 weeks

# Budget:

1. Project initiation and planning: $5,000
2. System design and architecture: $10,000
3. Development: $60,000
4. Testing and quality assurance: $10,000
5. Deployment and integration: $5,000
6. User training and documentation: $5,000
7. Monitoring and maintenance: $2,000 per month

Total estimated project cost: $95,000 (excluding ongoing maintenance)

# Risks and Mitigation:

1. Scope creep: Clearly define project scope and objectives, and establish a change control process to manage any changes to the project scope.
2. Technical challenges: Ensure that the development team has the necessary skills and expertise to address any technical challenges that may arise.
3. Integration with corporate systems: Collaborate closely with the IT department to ensure seamless integration with existing systems and infrastructure.
4. Legal and regulatory compliance: Consult with legal and compliance teams to ensure that the system adheres to all applicable data protection and privacy regulations.
5. User adoption: Provide comprehensive training and support to employees and managers to ensure successful adoption of the system.